name: Mickey Takes Over 2...
description:
After Mickey bought Earth People started to realise his plan and tried to escape to other planets to avoid being puppets in Mickeys scheme. But will you save the humans, or will you choose to continue to buy the planets to light Mickeys fire once again?

Human Goal: Buy a big lazer to try and destroy Mickeys main planet (Earth)

Mickey Goal: Try and buy and own all planets before the humans stop you
